name: Prayer of Healing
level: 2
school: evocation
casting_time: minutes 10
range: feet 30
has_v_component
duration: instant
description: "Up to six creatures of your choice that you can see within range each regain hit points equal to 2d8 + your spellcasting ability modifier. This spell has no effect on undead or constructs."
upcast_description: "When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, the healing increases by 1d8 for each slot level above 2nd."
